Travelodge Appoints Gerald Lawless as non-Executive Director

-- B y   C o l m   H e a t l e y
-- 
2011-04-20T00:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/travelodge-appoints-gerald-lawless-as-non-executive-director.html
Travelodge Ltd. appointed Gerald Lawless as a non-executive director and he will take up the post
on May 3, the company said today in an e-mailed statement.  Lawless is executive chairman of Dubai-based hotel
management company, Jumeirah Group and also had a 23-year career
with Forte Hotels, where he managed hotels in the U.K. and  South
Africa , Travelodge said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
